    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-07-10</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-05-08T15:31:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Climate Risk Disclosure Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) to&nbsp;require an issuer of securities to annually disclose information regarding climate change-related risks posed to the issuer, including an issuer's strategies and actions to mitigate these risks.</p> <p>Among other things, issuers must (1) report their direct and indirect greenhouse-gas emissions, (2) disclose their fossil fuel-related assets, and (3) establish standards regarding the social cost of carbon.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
